definitions.definition: A mythical human of very great size.

subdefinitions.definition: Any of the gigantes , the race of giants in the Greek mythology.

definitions.definition: A very tall and large person.
A tall species of a particular animal or plant.
A star that is considerably more luminous than a main sequence star of the same temperature (e.g. red giant , blue giant ).
An Ethernet packet that exceeds the medium's maximum packet size of 1,518 bytes .

examples: The retail giant is set to acquire two more struggling high-street chains.

definitions.definition: A person of extraordinary strength or powers, bodily or intellectual .
A maneuver involving a full rotation around an axis while fully extended.
